#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events.rst:46
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:3
msgid "Registration Desk"
msgstr "Registracijska miza"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events.rst:46
msgid ""
"Instantly grant access to event attendees with Odoo's Registration Desk "
"feature."
msgstr ""
"Takoj dodelite dostop udeležencem dogodka s funkcijo Odoo Registracijska "
"miza."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events.rst:51
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_reporting/revenues_report.rst:3
msgid "Revenues report"
msgstr "Poročilo o prihodkih"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events.rst:51
msgid "Analyze the financial success of events with Odoo."
msgstr "Analizirajte finančni uspeh dogodkov z Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience.rst:6
msgid "Attendee experience"
msgstr "Izkušnja udeleženca"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:3
msgid "Community Chat Rooms"
msgstr "Skupnostne klepetalnice"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:5
msgid ""
"In the **Events** app, users can create *Jitsi* video conference rooms for "
"event attendees to connect and discuss topics related to the event."
msgstr ""
"V aplikaciji **Dogodki** lahko uporabniki ustvarijo videokonferenčne sobe "
"*Jitsi*, kjer se udeleženci dogodka povežejo in razpravljajo o temah, "
"povezanih z dogodkom."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:9
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:9
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:9
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:9
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:14
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:46
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Nastavitve"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:11
msgid ""
"To set up community rooms, the *Community Chat Rooms* feature needs to be "
"enabled in the **Events** settings by navigating to :menuselection:`Events "
"app --> Configuration --> Settings`. In the *Events* section, "
"enable :guilabel:`Community Chat Rooms` and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Za nastavitev skupnostnih sob je treba v nastavitvah **Dogodki** omogočiti "
"funkcijo *Skupnostne klepetalnice* tako, da pojdete na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Dogodki --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`. V "
"razdelku *Dogodki* omogočite :guilabel:`Skupnostne klepetalnice` in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:15
msgid ""
"With the *Community Chat Rooms* feature enabled, users can then :ref:`create "
"community rooms <community_rooms/create-room>` in the database and publish "
"them on the website. Event attendees can not only join rooms but also create "
"them directly :ref:`on the website <community_rooms/website>`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je funkcija *Skupnostne klepetalnice* omogočena, lahko uporabniki nato "
":ref:`ustvarijo skupnostne sobe <community_rooms/create-room>` v bazi "
"podatkov in jih objavijo na spletnem mestu. Udeleženci dogodka lahko ne samo "
"pridružijo sobam, ampak jih tudi neposredno ustvarijo :ref:`na spletnem "
"mestu <community_rooms/website>`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:22
msgid "Create a room"
msgstr "Ustvarite sobo"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:24
msgid ""
"To create a community room in the database, open the **Events** app, then "
"select or create an event."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti skupnostno sobo v bazi podatkov, odprite aplikacijo "
"**Dogodki** in izberite ali ustvarite dogodek."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:26
msgid ""
"A :icon:`fa-comments-o` :guilabel:`Rooms` smart button appears at the top of "
"the event form. Click it to open the list of meeting rooms created for the "
"event."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu obrazca dogodka se pojavi pameten gumb :icon:`fa-comments-o` "
":guilabel:`Sobe`. Kliknite nanj, da odprete seznam klepetalnic, ustvarjenih "
"za dogodek."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:None
msgid "List of meeting rooms for an event in Odoo Events."
msgstr "Seznam klepetalnic za dogodek v aplikaciji Odoo Dogodki."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:33
msgid "Meeting room form"
msgstr "Obrazec klepetalnice"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:35
msgid ""
"To create a new room, click :guilabel:`New`. This opens a form to configure "
"details about the room."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti novo sobo, kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`. S tem se odpre "
"obrazec za konfiguracijo podrobnosti o sobi."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:None
msgid "Meeting room form in Odoo Events."
msgstr "Obrazec klepetalnice v aplikaciji Odoo Dogodki."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:40
msgid "Begin by entering the name of the topic in the :guilabel:`Topic` field."
msgstr "Začnite z vnosom imena teme v polje :guilabel:`Tema`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:42
msgid "Then, complete the information in the following fields:"
msgstr "Nato izpolnite informacije v naslednjih poljih:"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:44
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Event`: Select the corresponding event for the meeting room. This "
"field is automatically populated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dogodek`: Izberite ustrezen dogodek za klepetalnico. To polje je "
"samodejno izpolnjeno."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Summary`: Enter a short description of the meeting room's purpose."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Povzetek`: Vnesite kratek opis namena klepetalnice."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:47
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Audience`: Specify the intended audience of the meeting room."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Občinstvo`: Navedite ciljno občinstvo klepetalnice."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:48
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Is Pinned`: Specify whether the meeting room should be pinned on "
"the event website."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Je pripeto`: Določite, ali naj bo soba za sestanke pripeta na "
"spletno stran dogodka."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:49
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Max capacity`: Select the maximum number of participants allowed "
"in the room."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Največja zmogljivost`: Izberite največje število udeležencev, "
"dovoljenih v sobi."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:50
msgid ":guilabel:`Language`: Select the language of the meeting."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Jezik`: Izberite jezik sestanka."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:52
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Chat Room` field is automatically populated with a generated "
"name for the *Jitsi* conference room. If desired, the user can change this "
"name by clicking the field and modifying any details on the resulting form."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Klepetalnica` se samodejno izpolni z ustvarjenim imenom za "
"konferenčno sobo *Jitsi*. Če želite, lahko uporabnik spremeni to ime s "
"klikom na polje in spreminjanjem podrobnosti v prikazanem obrazcu."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:56
msgid ""
"Finally, the :guilabel:`Participant count` field automatically populates "
"with the number of attendees currently in the meeting room."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Število udeležencev` se samodejno izpolni s številom "
"udeležencev, ki so trenutno v sobi za sestanke."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:59
msgid ""
"Once the meeting room form is complete, a :guilabel:`Reporting` tab appears "
"at the bottom of the form, allowing users to monitor the :guilabel:`Last "
"activity` date and the :guilabel:`Peak participants` count for the event."
msgstr ""
"Ko je obrazec sobe za sestanke dokončan, se na dnu obrazca prikaže zavihek "
":guilabel:`Poročanje`, ki uporabnikom omogoča spremljanje datuma "
":guilabel:`Zadnja aktivnost` in števila :guilabel:`Najvišje število "
"udeležencev` za dogodek."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:64
msgid "Publish meeting room"
msgstr "Objavi sobo za sestanke"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:66
msgid ""
"After configuring the meeting room form, users must publish the room on the "
"event website to make it visible for event attendees. To do this, click "
"the :icon:`fa-globe` :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart button at the top of "
"the meeting room form."
msgstr ""
"Po konfiguraciji obrazca sobe za sestanke morajo uporabniki objaviti sobo na "
"spletni strani dogodka, da bo vidna udeležencem dogodka. To storite tako, da "
"kliknete pametni gumb :icon:`fa-globe` :guilabel:`Pojdi na spletno stran` na "
"vrhu obrazca sobe za sestanke."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:70
msgid ""
"This opens the meeting room page on the event website, currently invisible "
"to attendees. To publish it, toggle the :icon:`fa-toggle-"
"off` :guilabel:`Unpublished` button. The meeting room is then :icon:`fa-"
"toggle-on` :guilabel:`Published` and available for attendees to join."
msgstr ""
"To odpre stran sobe za sestanke na spletni strani dogodka, ki je trenutno "
"nevidna udeležencem. Za objavo preklopite gumb :icon:`fa-toggle-off` "
":guilabel:`Neobjavljeno`. Soba za sestanke je nato :icon:`fa-toggle-on` "
":guilabel:`Objavljeno` in na voljo udeležencem za pridružitev."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:77
msgid "Community rooms on the website"
msgstr "Skupnostne sobe na spletni strani"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:79
msgid ""
"Once published, community rooms appear on the event's webpage. To access "
"them, open the **Website** app and navigate to the :guilabel:`Events` header "
"menu item on the website. Then, select the desired event to open the event-"
"specific webpage. The sub-menu appears with the :guilabel:`Community` option."
msgstr ""
"Ko so objavljene, se skupnostne sobe prikažejo na spletni strani dogodka. Za "
"dostop do njih odprite aplikacijo **Spletna stran** in se na spletni strani "
"pomaknite do elementa menija glave :guilabel:`Dogodki`. Nato izberite želeni "
"dogodek, da odprete spletno stran, specifično za dogodek. Prikaže se podmeni "
"z možnostjo :guilabel:`Skupnost`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:85
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Community` sub-menu item is not displayed, the website "
"must first be modified in the database using the editor mode in order to "
"display the sub-menu."
msgstr ""
"Če element podmenija :guilabel:`Skupnost` ni prikazan, je treba spletno "
"stran najprej spremeniti v zbirki podatkov z uporabo urejevalnega načina, da "
"se podmeni prikaže."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:88
msgid ""
"To start, click :guilabel:`Edit` in the top corner. In "
"the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, toggle the :guilabel:`Sub-menu (Specific)` "
"option, then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Za začetek kliknite :guilabel:`Uredi` v zgornjem kotu. V zavihku "
":guilabel:`Prilagodi` preklopite možnost :guilabel:`Podmeni (specifično)`, "
"nato kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:None
msgid "Meeting rooms page on event webpage in Odoo Events."
msgstr "Stran sob za sestanke na spletni strani dogodka v Odoo Events."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:94
msgid ""
"Clicking the :guilabel:`Community` sub-menu item opens the *Join a room* "
"page, listing all published meeting rooms, along with information including "
"the topic title, a short summary of the room's purpose, and the number of "
"participants in the room. Optionally, attendees can also pin a meeting room "
"by clicking the :icon:`fa-thumb-tack` :guilabel:`(pin)` icon next to the "
"title."
msgstr ""
"Klik na element podmenija :guilabel:`Skupnost` odpre stran *Pridruži se "
"sobi*, ki prikazuje vse objavljene sobe za sestanke skupaj z informacijami, "
"vključno z naslovom teme, kratkim povzetkom namena sobe in številom "
"udeležencev v sobi. Po želji lahko udeleženci tudi pripnejo sobo za sestanke "
"s klikom na ikono :icon:`fa-thumb-tack` :guilabel:`(pripni)` poleg naslova."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:99
msgid ""
"To join a room, click on the desired topic. This opens the *Jitsi* video "
"conferencing room where attendees can chat."
msgstr ""
"Za pridružitev sobi kliknite na želeno temo. To odpre videokonferenčno sobo "
"*Jitsi*, kjer lahko udeleženci klepetajo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:None
msgid "Meeting room on event webpage in Odoo Events."
msgstr "Soba za sestanke na spletni strani dogodka v Odoo Events."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:106
msgid "Create a room as an attendee"
msgstr "Ustvarite sobo kot udeleženec"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:108
msgid ""
"The *Join a room* page on the event website also features an option for "
"attendees to launch a new meeting room for a specific topic."
msgstr ""
"Stran *Pridruži se sobi* na spletni strani dogodka prav tako ponuja možnost, "
"da udeleženci zaženejo novo sobo za sestanke za določeno temo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:111
msgid ""
"To create a new meeting room as an attendee, click the :guilabel:`Create a "
"Room` button. This opens a *Launch a new topic* pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje nove sobe za sestanke kot udeleženec kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Ustvari sobo`. To odpre pojavno okno *Zaženi novo temo*."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:114
msgid ""
"Similar to creating a room in the database, continue by filling in the "
"following details about the room:"
msgstr ""
"Podobno kot pri ustvarjanju sobe v podatkovni bazi nadaljujte z izpolnitvijo "
"naslednjih podrobnosti o sobi:"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:117
msgid ":guilabel:`Room Topic`: The name of the topic."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tema sobe`: Ime teme."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Short Summary`: A short description about the meeting's purpose."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kratek povzetek`: Kratek opis namena sestanka."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:119
msgid ":guilabel:`Target People`: The intended audience of the meeting."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ciljna publika`: Predvideno občinstvo sestanka."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:120
msgid ":guilabel:`Language`: The target language of the meeting."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Jezik`: Ciljni jezik sestanka."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:121
msgid ":guilabel:`Capacity`: The maximum capacity of the room."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Zmogljivost`: Največja zmogljivost sobe."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/community_rooms.rst:123
msgid ""
"After completing the form, click :guilabel:`Create` to finish. The room is "
"then created and the attendee is redirected to the conferencing page."
msgstr ""
"Po izpolnitvi obrazca kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari`, da zaključite. Soba je "
"nato ustvarjena in udeleženec je preusmerjen na stran za konferenco."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo **Events** provides users the ability to create, schedule, and manage "
"*tracks*, which are talks, lectures, presentations, etc."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Dogodki** uporabnikom zagotavlja možnost ustvarjanja, načrtovanja in "
"upravljanja *predavanj*, ki so govori, predavanja, predstavitve itd."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:11
msgid ""
"To enable tracks in Odoo, navigate to :menuselection:`Events app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and tick the checkbox beside "
"the :guilabel:`Schedule & Tracks` setting."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti predavanja v Odoo, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Dogodki --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in potrdite "
"potrditveno polje poleg nastavitve :guilabel:`Urnik in predavanja`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Schedule and Tracks setting in the Odoo Events app, along with "
"corresponding options."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev Urnik in sledi v aplikaciji Odoo Dogodki skupaj z ustreznimi "
"možnostmi."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:17
msgid ""
"Once the setting is selected, two additional configuration options appear "
"beneath it:"
msgstr ""
"Ko je nastavitev izbrana, se pod njo prikažeta dve dodatni možnosti "
"konfiguracije:"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:19
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Live Broadcast`: :ref:`Broadcast tracks online <events/additional-"
"configs/live-broadcasting>` through a *YouTube* integration."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prenos v živo`: :ref:`Prenašajte sledi v živo <events/additional-"
"configs/live-broadcasting>` prek integracije z *YouTubom*."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:21
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Event Gamification`: :ref:`Share quizzes with attendees <events/"
"additional-configs/event-gamification>` after a track concludes."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Igrifikacija dogodka`: :ref:`Delite kvize z udeleženci <events/"
"additional-configs/event-gamification>` po zaključku sledi."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:24
msgid ""
"Once all desired settings have been enabled, click the :guilabel:`Save` "
"button in the upper-left corner of the :guilabel:`Settings` page."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vse želene nastavitve omogočene, kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Shrani` v "
"zgornjem levem kotu strani :guilabel:`Nastavitve`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:30
msgid "Event tracks dashboard"
msgstr "Nadzorna plošča sledi dogodka"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:32
msgid ""
"To access, modify, and/or create tracks for an event, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Events app`, and either select an existing event from "
"the :guilabel:`Events` dashboard or :doc:`create a new one <../event_setup/"
"create_events>`."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop, spreminjanje in/ali ustvarjanje sledi za dogodek se pomaknite na "
":menuselection:`aplikacijo Dogodki` in izberite obstoječi dogodek z nadzorne "
"plošče :guilabel:`Dogodki` ali :doc:`ustvarite novega <../event_setup/"
"create_events>`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:36
msgid ""
"On the selected event form, click the :guilabel:`Tracks` smart button at the "
"top to land on the :guilabel:`Event Tracks` page, which presents all the "
"tracks (both scheduled and proposed) for the event."
msgstr ""
"Na obrazcu izbranega dogodka kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Sledi` na "
"vrhu, da pridete na stran :guilabel:`Sledi dogodka`, ki prikazuje vse sledi "
"(tako načrtovane kot predlagane) za dogodek."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:43
msgid "Views"
msgstr "Pogledi"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:45
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Event Tracks` page can be displayed in six different views:"
msgstr ""
"Stran :guilabel:`Sledi dogodka` je mogoče prikazati v šestih različnih "
"pogledih:"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:49
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_reporting/attendees_report.rst:58
msgid "Kanban"
msgstr "Kanban"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:51
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`Event Tracks` page opens in the :icon:`oi-view-"
"kanban` :guilabel:`(Kanban)` view, providing users an at-a-glance overview "
"of all tracks for the selected event."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto se stran :guilabel:`Sledi dogodka` odpre v pogledu :icon:`oi-view-"
"kanban` :guilabel:`(Kanban)`, ki uporabnikom nudi hiter pregled vseh sledi "
"za izbrani dogodek."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:0
msgid "Typical event tracks page for an event in the Odoo Events application."
msgstr "Tipična stran sledi dogodka za dogodek v aplikaciji Odoo Dogodki."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:58
msgid ""
"In the default :icon:`oi-view-kanban` :guilabel:`(Kanban)` view, the tracks "
"are categorized into several modifiable "
"stages: :guilabel:`Proposal` :guilabel:`Confirmed`, :guilabel:`Announced`, :guilabel:`Published`, :guilabel:`Refused` "
"(collapsed), and :guilabel:`Cancelled` (collapsed)."
msgstr ""
"V privzetem pogledu :icon:`oi-view-kanban` :guilabel:`(Kanban)` so sledi "
"razvrščene v več spremenljivih faz: :guilabel:`Predlog`, "
":guilabel:`Potrjeno`, :guilabel:`Najavljeno`, :guilabel:`Objavljeno`, "
":guilabel:`Zavrnjeno` (strnjeno) in :guilabel:`Preklicano` (strnjeno)."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:63
msgid ""
"Records displayed in the Kanban can be narrowed down using :ref:`grouping "
"<events/tracks-dashboard/group>` and :ref:`filter <events/tracks-dashboard/"
"filter>` options."
msgstr ""
"Zapise, prikazane v pogledu Kanban, je mogoče zožiti z možnostmi "
":ref:`združevanja <events/tracks-dashboard/group>` in :ref:`filtriranja "
"<events/tracks-dashboard/filter>`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:66
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_reporting/attendees_report.rst:75
msgid ""
"For more information about using the Kanban view, see the :ref:`Kanban "
"<studio/views/multiple-records/kanban>` documentation."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o uporabi pogleda Kanban si oglejte dokumentacijo "
":ref:`Kanban <studio/views/multiple-records/kanban>`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:69
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_reporting/attendees_report.rst:78
