msgstr ""
"Zapise, prikazane v pogledu Seznam, je mogoče zožiti z možnostmi "
":ref:`združevanja <events/tracks-dashboard/group>` in :ref:`filtriranja "
"<events/tracks-dashboard/filter>`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:82
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_reporting/attendees_report.rst:91
