msgstr "`Odoo vodniki: Marketing <https://www.odoo.com/slides/marketing-27>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:20
msgid ""
"`Magic Sheet - Marketing Automation [PDF] <https://drive.google.com/drive/"
"folders/1MMMGcYIG1tm160jC2JaXVc_D5b6x3cJd>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Čarobni list - Marketing Automation [PDF] <https://drive.google.com/drive/"
"folders/1MMMGcYIG1tm160jC2JaXVc_D5b6x3cJd>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:25
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/target_audience.rst:3
msgid "Audience targeting"
msgstr "Ciljanje občinstva"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:25
msgid "Configure the target audience for a campaign."
msgstr "Konfigurirajte ciljno občinstvo za kampanjo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:30
msgid "Workflow activities"
msgstr "Aktivnosti poteka dela"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:30
msgid "Define the activities that occur within a campaign."
msgstr "Določite aktivnosti, ki se izvajajo znotraj kampanje."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:35
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/testing_running.rst:3
msgid "Testing/running campaigns"
msgstr "Testiranje/izvajanje kampanj"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:35
msgid "Launch a test or run a campaign."
msgstr "Zaženite testni ali izvedite kampanjo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:40
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/understanding_metrics.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_card.rst:194
msgid "Campaign metrics"
msgstr "Metrike kampanje"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:40
msgid "Review the metrics of a campaign."
msgstr "Preglejte metrike kampanje."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:48
msgid ""
"To begin, make sure the **Marketing Automation** application "
"is :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Za začetek se prepričaj, da je aplikacija **Marketing Automation** "
":ref:`nameščena <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:51
msgid ""
"Installing the **Marketing Automation** application also installs "
"the :doc:`Email Marketing <email_marketing>` app, as most features of Odoo "
"**Marketing Automation** are dependent on that specific application."
msgstr ""
"Namestitev aplikacije **Marketing Automation** namesti tudi aplikacijo "
":doc:`Email Marketing <email_marketing>`, saj je večina funkcij Odoo "
"**Marketing Automation** odvisna od te določene aplikacije."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:55
msgid ""
"Additionally, install the :doc:`CRM <../sales/crm>` and :doc:`SMS Marketing "
"<sms_marketing>` applications to access *all* of the features available in "
"**Marketing Automation**."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega namesti aplikaciji :doc:`CRM <../sales/crm>` in :doc:`SMS "
"Marketing <sms_marketing>`, da dostopaš do *vseh* funkcij, ki so na voljo v "
"**Marketing Automation**."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:58
msgid ""
"The following documentation assumes that all three of these dependent "
"applications are installed on the database."
msgstr ""
"Naslednja dokumentacija predpostavlja, da so vse tri od teh odvisnih "
"aplikacij nameščene v bazi podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:64
msgid "Campaigns"
msgstr "Kampanje"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:66
msgid ""
"A *campaign* refers to a workflow of activities that are automatically "
"executed to a target audience, based on predefined filters, triggers, and "
"durations of activities."
msgstr ""
"*Kampanja* se nanaša na potek dela dejavnosti, ki se samodejno izvajajo za "
"ciljno občinstvo na podlagi vnaprej določenih filtrov, sprožilcev in trajanj "
"dejavnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:69
msgid ""
"A new campaign can be created from scratch or from a :ref:`template "
"<marketing_automation/campaign-templates>`."
msgstr ""
"Nova kampanja se lahko ustvari od začetka ali iz :ref:`predloge "
"<marketing_automation/campaign-templates>`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:72
msgid ""
"To create a campaign, navigate to the :menuselection:`Marketing Automation` "
"application and click the :guilabel:`New` button to reveal a new campaign "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje kampanje pojdi na aplikacijo :menuselection:`Marketing "
"Automation` in klikni gumb :guilabel:`Novo`, da prikažeš nov obrazec "
"kampanje."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:78
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates.rst:5
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/marketing_campaigns.rst:82
msgid "Campaign templates"
msgstr "Predloge kampanj"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:80
msgid ""
"Odoo provides six campaign templates to help users get started. The campaign "
"template cards **only** display when there are no existing campaigns in the "
"database. Once a campaign has been created, the template cards on the "
"*Campaigns* dashboard are replaced with a Kanban view of the existing "
"campaigns."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ponuja šest predlog kampanj, ki uporabnikom pomagajo pri začetku. "
"Kartice predlog kampanj se prikažejo **samo**, ko v bazi podatkov ni "
"obstoječih kampanj. Ko je kampanja ustvarjena, so kartice predlog na "
"nadzorni plošči *Kampanje* zamenjane s pogledom Kanban obstoječih kampanj."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:85
msgid ""
"To get started with a template, navigate to the :menuselection:`Marketing "
"Automation` application, from the main Odoo dashboard, to open "
"the :guilabel:`Campaigns` dashboard, which displays six :doc:`campaign "
"template <marketing_automation/campaign_templates>` cards:"
msgstr ""
"Za začetek s predlogo se pomaknite do aplikacije "
":menuselection:`Avtomatizacija trženja` z glavne Odoo nadzorne plošče, da "
"odprete nadzorno ploščo :guilabel:`Kampanje`, ki prikazuje šest kartic "
":doc:`predlog kampanj <marketing_automation/campaign_templates>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:0
msgid ":icon:`fa-tag` :guilabel:`Tag Hot Contacts`"
msgstr ":icon:`fa-tag` :guilabel:`Označi vroče stike`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:0
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Send a welcome email to contacts and tag them if they click it.`"
msgstr ""
