#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:None
msgid ""
"Six campaign template cards on the Campaigns dashboard of the Marketing "
"Automation app."
msgstr ""
"Šest kartic predlog kampanj na nadzorni plošči Kampanje aplikacije "
"Avtomatizacija trženja."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:106
msgid ""
"These templates are designed to be used as starting points for creating new "
"campaigns. Click one of the template cards to open the campaign form."
msgstr ""
"Te predloge so zasnovane kot izhodišča za ustvarjanje novih kampanj. "
"Kliknite eno od kartic predlog, da odprete obrazec kampanje."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:110
msgid ""
"To display the campaign template cards again after a campaign has been "
"created, type the name of a campaign that does **not** exist in the database "
"into the search bar, then press :kbd:`Enter`."
msgstr ""
"Za ponoven prikaz kartic predlog kampanj po tem, ko je bila kampanja "
"ustvarjena, vnesite ime kampanje, ki v bazi podatkov **ne** obstaja, v "
"iskalno vrstico in pritisnite :kbd:`Enter`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:113
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates/double_optin.rst:33
msgid ""
"For example, searching for `empty` displays the campaign template cards "
"again, as long as there is not a campaign with the name \"empty\" in the "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, iskanje `empty` ponovno prikaže kartice predlog kampanj, dokler v "
"bazi podatkov ni kampanje z imenom \"empty\"."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:117
msgid "Targets and filters"
msgstr "Cilji in filtri"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:119
msgid ""
"On the campaign form, the :guilabel:`Target` and :guilabel:`Filter` section, "
"also referred to as the domain, contains the fields used to define the "
"target audience for the campaign's reach (i.e., the unique contact records "
"in the database)."
msgstr ""
"V obrazcu kampanje odsek :guilabel:`Cilj` in :guilabel:`Filter`, imenovan "
"tudi domena, vsebuje polja, uporabljena za opredelitev ciljne publike za "
"doseg kampanje (tj. edinstvene zapise stikov v bazi podatkov)."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:123
msgid ""
"The target audience specifies the type of records available for use in the "
"campaign, such as *Lead/Opportunity*, *Event Registration*, *Contact*, and "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Ciljna publika določa vrsto zapisov, ki so na voljo za uporabo v kampanji, "
"kot so *Potencialna stranka/Priložnost*, *Registracija dogodka*, *Stik* in "
"še več."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:127
msgid "Records"
msgstr "Zapisi"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:129
msgid ""
"The contacts in the system that fit the specified criteria for a campaign "
"are referred to as *records*."
msgstr ""
"Stiki v sistemu, ki ustrezajo določenim kriterijem za kampanjo, se imenujejo "
"*zapisi*."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:132
msgid ""
"The number of records that are displayed next to the "
"campaign :guilabel:`Filter` represent the total number of records the "
"campaign is targeting."
msgstr ""
"Število zapisov, prikazanih poleg :guilabel:`Filtra` kampanje, predstavlja "
"skupno število zapisov, ki jih kampanja cilja."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:136
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/understanding_metrics.rst:157
msgid "Participants"
msgstr "Udeleženci"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:138
msgid ""
"The records that are engaged by the campaign are referred to as "
"*participants*."
msgstr "Zapisi, ki so vključeni v kampanjo, se imenujejo *udeleženci*."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:140
msgid ""
"The number of participants engaged in a test run are shown in the *Tests* "
"smart button, which displays on the top of the campaign form after a test "
"has been run."
msgstr ""
"Število udeležencev, vključenih v testni potek, je prikazano v pametnem "
"gumbu *Testi*, ki se prikaže na vrhu obrazca kampanje po izvedbi testa."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:143
msgid ""
"The number of participants engaged in a running, or stopped, campaign are "
"shown in the *Participants* smart button at the top of the campaign form."
msgstr ""
"Število udeležencev, vključenih v tekočo ali ustavljeno kampanjo, je "
"prikazano v pametnem gumbu *Udeleženci* na vrhu obrazca kampanje."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:147
msgid ":doc:`Audience targeting <marketing_automation/target_audience>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Ciljanje publike <marketing_automation/target_audience>`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:150
msgid "Workflow"
msgstr "Delovni tok"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:152
msgid ""
"A *workflow* consists of an activity, many activities, or a sequence of "
"activities organized in a campaign. A campaign's workflow is defined in "
"the :guilabel:`Workflow` section of the campaign form."
msgstr ""
"*Potek dela* je sestavljen iz aktivnosti, več aktivnosti ali zaporedja "
"aktivnosti, organiziranih v kampanji. Potek dela kampanje je določen v "
"razdelku :guilabel:`Potek dela` obrazca kampanje."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:156
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/workflow_activities.rst:19
msgid "Activities"
msgstr "Aktivnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:158
msgid ""
"*Activities* are the methods of communication or server actions, organized "
"in a workflow, that are executed within a campaign. Once running, each "
"activity displays the number of participants that are engaged by the "
"activity as *Success* and *Rejected* counts."
msgstr ""
"*Aktivnosti* so načini komunikacije ali dejanja strežnika, organizirana v "
"poteku dela, ki se izvajajo v kampanji. Ko teče kampanja, vsaka aktivnost "
"prikaže število udeležencev, vključenih v aktivnost, kot število *Uspešnih* "
"in *Zavrnjenih*."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:162
msgid ""
"To create one of the following activities, click :guilabel:`Add new "
"activity` in the :guilabel:`Workflow` section of the campaign form:"
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje ene od naslednjih aktivnosti kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj novo "
"aktivnost` v razdelku :guilabel:`Potek dela` obrazca kampanje:"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:165
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/workflow_activities.rst:53
msgid ""
":ref:`Email <marketing_automation/email-activity-type>`: an email that is "
"sent to the target audience."
msgstr ""
":ref:`E-pošta <marketing_automation/email-activity-type>`: e-poštno "
"sporočilo, poslano ciljni publiki."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:167
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/workflow_activities.rst:55
msgid ""
":ref:`Server action <marketing_automation/sa-activity-type>`: an internal "
"action within the database that is executed."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Dejanje strežnika <marketing_automation/sa-activity-type>`: interno "
"dejanje v zbirki podatkov, ki se izvede."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:169
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/workflow_activities.rst:57
msgid ""
":ref:`SMS <marketing_automation/sms-activity-type>`: a text message that is "
"sent to the target audience."
msgstr ""
":ref:`SMS <marketing_automation/sms-activity-type>`: besedilno sporočilo, "
"poslano ciljni publiki."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:173
msgid ":doc:`marketing_automation/workflow_activities`"
msgstr ":doc:`marketing_automation/workflow_activities`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:176
msgid "Testing and running"
msgstr "Testiranje in zagon"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:178
msgid ""
"Once a campaign has been created, it can be tested to ensure the workflow is "
"functioning as expected, to check for errors, and correct any mistakes "
"before it reaches its target audience."
msgstr ""
"Ko je kampanja ustvarjena, jo je mogoče testirati, da se preveri, ali potek "
"dela deluje po pričakovanjih, da se preverijo napake in popravijo morebitne "
"pomanjkljivosti, preden doseže ciljno publiko."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:181
msgid ""
"After testing, the campaign can be launched to start engaging the target "
"audience. The campaign can also be launched *without* testing, if the user "
"is confident in the workflow."
msgstr ""
"Po testiranju je kampanjo mogoče zagnati, da se začne vključevanje ciljne "
"publike. Kampanjo je mogoče zagnati tudi *brez* testiranja, če je uporabnik "
"prepričan v potek dela."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:185
msgid ":doc:`marketing_automation/testing_running`"
msgstr ":doc:`marketing_automation/testing_running`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:190
msgid ""
"A range of reporting metrics are available to measure the success of each "
"campaign. Navigate to :menuselection:`Marketing Automation app --> "
"Reporting` to access the following menu options:"
msgstr ""
"Na voljo je vrsta poročevalskih metrik za merjenje uspeha posamezne "
"kampanje. Pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Marketing Automation --> "
"Poročanje`, da dostopate do naslednjih možnosti menija:"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:193
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Link Tracker`: displays the metrics of links to track the number "
"of clicks."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sledilnik povezav`: prikazuje metrike povezav za sledenje številu "
"klikov."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:194
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Traces`: displays the results of all activities from all "
"campaigns."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Sledi`: prikaže rezultate vseh dejavnosti iz vseh kampanj."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:195
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Participants`: displays an overview of the participants of all "
"campaigns."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Udeleženci`: prikaže pregled udeležencev vseh kampanj."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:197
msgid ""
"Additionally, each activity within the workflow of a campaign displays its "
"engagement metrics."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega vsaka dejavnost v poteku dela kampanje prikaže svoje metrike "
"vključenosti."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation.rst:200
msgid ":doc:`marketing_automation/understanding_metrics`"
msgstr ":doc:`marketing_automation/understanding_metrics`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates/double_optin.rst:3
msgid "Double Opt-in"
msgstr "Dvojna prijava"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates/double_optin.rst:5
msgid ""
"A *double opt-in*, also referred to as a *confirmed opt-in*, may be required "
"in some countries for marketing communications, due to anti-SPAM laws. "
"Confirming consent has several other benefits, as well: it validates email "
"addresses, avoids spam/robo subscribers, keeps mailing lists clean, and only "
"includes engaged contacts in the mailing list."
msgstr ""
"*Dvojna privolitev*, znana tudi kot *potrjena privolitev*, je lahko v "
"nekaterih državah zahtevana za trženjska sporočila zaradi zakonov proti "
"neželeni pošti. Potrjevanje privolitve ima še več drugih prednosti: potrjuje "
"e-poštne naslove, preprečuje neželene/robotske naročnike, ohranja sezname "
"prejemnikov čiste in vključuje samo vključene stike na seznam prejemnikov."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates/double_optin.rst:10
msgid ""
"When the *Double Opt-in* campaign template is used, a new mailing list "
"titled, *Confirmed contacts* is created in the *Email Marketing* app, and "
"any new mailing list contacts that are added to the default *Newsletter* "
"mailing list are sent a confirmation email to double opt-in. The contacts "
"that click on the confirmation link in the email are automatically added to "
"the *Confirmed contacts* mailing list in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Ko se uporabi predloga kampanje *Dvojna privolitev*, se v aplikaciji *E-"
"poštno trženje* ustvari nov seznam prejemnikov z naslovom *Potrjeni stiki*, "
"vsem novim stikom s seznama prejemnikov, ki so dodani na privzeti seznam "
"prejemnikov *Novice*, pa se pošlje e-poštno sporočilo s potrditvijo za "
"dvojno privolitev. Stiki, ki kliknejo na povezavo za potrditev v e-poštnem "
"sporočilu, so samodejno dodani na seznam prejemnikov *Potrjeni stiki* v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates/double_optin.rst:17
msgid ""
"When using the *Double Opt-in* campaign template, only the contacts in the "
"*Confirmed contacts mailing* list are considered to have confirmed their "
"consent."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi predloge kampanje *Dvojna privolitev* se šteje, da so samo stiki "
"na seznamu *Potrjeni stiki* potrdili svojo privolitev."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates/double_optin.rst:23
msgid "Use the Double Opt-in campaign template"
msgstr "Uporaba predloge kampanje Dvojna privolitev"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates/double_optin.rst:25
msgid ""
"Open the :menuselection:`Marketing Automation` app, and select "
"the :guilabel:`Double Opt-in` campaign template to create a new campaign for "
"confirming consent."
msgstr ""
"Odprite aplikacijo :menuselection:`Marketing Automation` in izberite "
"predlogo kampanje :guilabel:`Double Opt-in`, da ustvarite novo kampanjo za "
"potrjevanje privolitve."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates/double_optin.rst:29
msgid ""
"The campaign templates do **not** display, by default, when there are "
"existing *Marketing Automation* campaigns. To display the campaign "
"templates, type the name of a campaign (that does not exist in the database) "
"into the :guilabel:`Search...` bar, then press :kbd:`Enter`."
msgstr ""
"Predloge kampanj se privzeto **ne** prikažejo, ko obstajajo kampanje "
"*Marketing Automation*. Za prikaz predlog kampanj vnesite ime kampanje (ki "
"ne obstaja v bazi podatkov) v iskalno vrstico :guilabel:`Search...` in "
"pritisnite :kbd:`Enter`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates/double_optin.rst:37
msgid "Campaign configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija kampanje"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates/double_optin.rst:39
msgid ""
"Upon creation of the campaign, the campaign form loads with a new "
"preconfigured campaign."
msgstr ""
"Ob ustvarjanju kampanje se naloži obrazec kampanje z novo vnaprej "
"konfigurirano kampanjo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates/double_optin.rst:41
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Target` and :guilabel:`Filter` configurations of the campaign "
"are as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Konfiguraciji :guilabel:`Target` in :guilabel:`Filter` kampanje sta "
"naslednji:"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates/double_optin.rst:43
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`: `Double Opt-in`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Name`: `Double Opt-in`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates/double_optin.rst:44
msgid ":guilabel:`Responsible`\\*: The user who created the campaign."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Responsible`\\*: Uporabnik, ki je ustvaril kampanjo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates/double_optin.rst:45
msgid ":guilabel:`Target`: :guilabel:`Mailing Contact`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Target`: :guilabel:`Mailing Contact`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/campaign_templates/double_optin.rst:46
msgid ":guilabel:`Unicity based on`: :guilabel:`Email (Mailing Contact)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Unicity based on`: :guilabel:`Email (Mailing Contact)`"

